<i>noun</i>: 청취 [청취], 듣기 [듣끼] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>청취 [청취]</dt><br>
<dd>listening</dd><br>
<dd>의견, 보고, 방송 등을 들음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of listening to an opinion, report, broadcast, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>듣기 [듣끼]</dt><br>
<dd>listening</dd><br>
<dd>남의 말을 올바르게 알아듣고 이해하는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The ability to listen to another person's words and understanding them.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>